gw.api.domain.accounting

Class ChargeReturnObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.api.domain.accounting.ChargeReturnObject

  • public class ChargeReturnObject
extends java.lang.Object
    A struct consisting of a small group of objects meant to be used as a return type. Its data members are: ChargePattern, MonetaryAmount, TAccountOwner and InvoicePayer. ChargePattern and MonetaryAmount are required. TAccountOwner and InvoicePayer are optional.
